Competition: Arab Club Champions Cup 
Season: 1998


Stage: Preliminary

*Automatically qualified: 
*Club Africain (Tunisia, holders), Al Ittihad (Saudi Arabia, hosts).

*Zone 1 (in Oman, February 1998):
*West Riffa (Bahrain) and Al Wasl (UAE) qualified in GCC Champions' Cup:

