*Zone 2 (in Cairo):
*Al Wahda (Yemen) and Al Merreikh (Sudan) withdrew.

; Al Ahli     ; 3-1; Al Shabah
; Al Ahli     ; 1-0; Al Shabab

*Al Ahli (Egypt) withdrew, Al Shabab (Saudi Arabia) qualified.

*Zone 3
*CA Bizertin (Tunisia) withdrew, WA Tlemcen (Algeria) and Al Tahaddy (Libya) qualified.

Zone: 4
*Teshrin (Syria), Palestine and Lebanese representatives withdrew, Al Wahdat (Jordan) qualified.


Stage: Final
*(Jeddah, Nov 19-30)

Group: A

Round 1 [Nov 19]
Al Ittihad    0-1 Al Wasl
Al Wahdat     2-2 Al Tahaddy
Round 2 [Nov 21]
Al Ittihad    3-1 Al Wahdat
Al Wasl       0-0 Al Tahaddy
Round 3 [Nov 24]
Al Ittihad    6-0 Al Tahaddy
Al Wasl       5-1 Al Wahdat

 
* 1.Al Wasl           3  2  1  0  6- 1  7  [UAE]
* 2.Al Ittihad        3  2  0  1  9- 2  6  [Jeddah, Saudi Arabia]
* 3.Al Tahaddy        3  0  2  1  2- 8  2  [Libya]
* 4.Al Wahdat         3  0  1  2  4-10  1  [Jordan]

Group: B

Round 1 [Nov 20]
WA Tlemcen    0-0 Al Shabab
Club Africain 0-3 West Riffa
Round 2 [Nov 22]
Al Shabab     2-1 West Riffa
WA Tlemcen    1-1 Club Africain
Round 3 [Nov 25]
Club Africain 1-1 Al Shabab
WA Tlemcen    2-1 West Riffa

