Round: Semifinals [Nov 27]

Al Wasl       1-3 WA Tlemcen 
Al Shabab     1-0 Al Ittihad

Round: Final [Nov 30]

Al Shabab     1-3 WA Tlemcen 

*WA Tlemcen winners 1998.


